channel.title: Easy, 2 Minute Passage Into World 1, 2, 3...18, And Other Worlds
channel.description:
Firts go into a note pad, and paste this code
<html><body><iframe src="http://ul8.runescape.com/l1,p0,j1" name="mainframe" width="800" height="550" scrolling="auto"> </iframe></body></html>
The next thing is to save that with ".html" in the end of the name it should look like this "w2.html"
when its saved it should appear a icon on ur desktop like a web page, with the name u used to save. When u doble clic on it, it should pop up a Internet explorer or fire fox windows with the loguing screen to the world u used.
If you wanna change the world to log in just change the "http://ul7.runescape.com/l1,p0,j0" link for the one u want and make all the steps again. Here is a list of the links of the world hard to join.
World 1: http://ul7.runescape.com/l1,p0,j0 World 2: http://ul8.runescape.com/l1,p0,j1 World 6: http://sl10.runescape.com/l1,p0,j0 World 9: http://abov4.runescape.com/l1,p0,j0 world18: http://nav2.runescape.com/l1,p0,j0 world22: http://nl1.runescape.com/l1,p0,j0
Note: This isnt ilegal, cuz we are not using any third program to make it easy, and we are only using windows to make it.
When saving, dont save it like "txt document" save it like " all documents"
